  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/258e7b576ebc52f833715154b4cefe17.poster.avif?t=1726634791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/258e7b576ebc52f833715154b4cefe17.webm?t=1726634791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/258e7b576ebc52f833715154b4cefe17.mp4?t=1726634791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Relaxicon helps you learn English and improve your vocabulary in a meditative way. Combine letters into words to get their definitions, score points, unlock over 70 types of challenges and enjoy original atmospheric background music and in-tune sound effects for a relaxing meditation.<br><br>Use mouse or keyboard to combine words together. Press Enter to score the word and get a definition.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/9f3df65a81e0cc988050254a8318fd6c.poster.avif?t=1726634791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/9f3df65a81e0cc988050254a8318fd6c.webm?t=1726634791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/9f3df65a81e0cc988050254a8318fd6c.mp4?t=1726634791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>If you made a mistake, use backspace to remove the last letter and continue typing the correct word.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/17d27fedf36dc1b93e01172b740e212a.poster.avif?t=1726634791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/17d27fedf36dc1b93e01172b740e212a.webm?t=1726634791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/17d27fedf36dc1b93e01172b740e212a.mp4?t=1726634791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Or press delete to break the whole word.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/6b1f8843dd49a8841c263f76d0be5b3f.poster.avif?t=1726634791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/6b1f8843dd49a8841c263f76d0be5b3f.webm?t=1726634791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/6b1f8843dd49a8841c263f76d0be5b3f.mp4?t=1726634791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>When you have a challenge, press space to toggle the description.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/c7375a3ae2ab5cb1dc164de0d490b384.poster.avif?t=1726634791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/c7375a3ae2ab5cb1dc164de0d490b384.webm?t=1726634791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/c7375a3ae2ab5cb1dc164de0d490b384.mp4?t=1726634791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Game contains <strong>over 130000 English word definitions!</strong><br><br>Soundtrack consists of <strong>9 original ambient pieces</strong>, and all sound effects were built specifically in tune with soundtrack, for maximum relaxation and ear pleasure.<br><br>Headphones are highly recommended.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/258e7b576ebc52f833715154b4cefe17.poster.avif?t=1726634791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/258e7b576ebc52f833715154b4cefe17.webm?t=1726634791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/258e7b576ebc52f833715154b4cefe17.mp4?t=1726634791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Relaxicon helps you learn English and improve your vocabulary in a meditative way. Combine letters into words to get their definitions, score points, unlock over 70 types of challenges and enjoy original atmospheric background music and in-tune sound effects for a relaxing meditation.<br><br>Use mouse or keyboard to combine words together. Press Enter to score the word and get a definition.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/9f3df65a81e0cc988050254a8318fd6c.poster.avif?t=1726634791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/9f3df65a81e0cc988050254a8318fd6c.webm?t=1726634791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/9f3df65a81e0cc988050254a8318fd6c.mp4?t=1726634791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>If you made a mistake, use backspace to remove the last letter and continue typing the correct word.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/17d27fedf36dc1b93e01172b740e212a.poster.avif?t=1726634791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/17d27fedf36dc1b93e01172b740e212a.webm?t=1726634791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/17d27fedf36dc1b93e01172b740e212a.mp4?t=1726634791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Or press delete to break the whole word.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/6b1f8843dd49a8841c263f76d0be5b3f.poster.avif?t=1726634791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/6b1f8843dd49a8841c263f76d0be5b3f.webm?t=1726634791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/6b1f8843dd49a8841c263f76d0be5b3f.mp4?t=1726634791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>When you have a challenge, press space to toggle the description.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/c7375a3ae2ab5cb1dc164de0d490b384.poster.avif?t=1726634791\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/c7375a3ae2ab5cb1dc164de0d490b384.webm?t=1726634791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815010/extras/c7375a3ae2ab5cb1dc164de0d490b384.mp4?t=1726634791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Game contains <strong>over 130000 English word definitions!</strong><br><br>Soundtrack consists of <strong>9 original ambient pieces</strong>, and all sound effects were built specifically in tune with soundtrack, for maximum relaxation and ear pleasure.<br><br>Headphones are highly recommended.",
